translation.Name: California Note - Government Virus Researching
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_8: Three days have passed since the beginning of the research, riots began in the city and it is simply impossible to work productively in such conditions. In addition to all this, the feds are putting pressure on us with deadlines. We just can not ... We are helpless over those who are not lucky to hide from this infection, but that is just how it is for now. Over the couse of last three days of research, all that we managed to understand is that this virus attacks though suppression of immunity system, and consequently kills the infected.
